frame.name: Luxury NFT Generator
frame.subtitle: Create premium NFT cards with blockchain minting
frame.description: Luxury NFT Generator lets you create stunning NFT cards with custom artwork, attributes, and rarity levels. Upload your image, customize stats, mint on multiple chains (Ethereum, Polygon, BSC), and download professional card designs with metadata.
frame.ogDescription: Design and mint stunning NFT cards with custom artwork, stats, and blockchain integration
